narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Good review of multiple radiometric isotope systems.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I think the course was great as it is. Perhaps a class or two with the basics at the very beginning could be helpful for those without any background.
Strengths: good papers, general course format. Weaknesses: could use more organized/critical discussion.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes. The class is a critical review of selected contemporary papers on different radiogenic isotopes' systems. I find those discussions very intellectually stimulating.
